COMPOSER
    1 - criar projeto (skeleton) / entrar no diretorio onde quer a instalacao

    composer create-project --stability='dev' zendframework/skeleton-application

    2 - colocando dependencia do zftool: so funciona no ZF2
    
    composer require zendframework/zftool:dev-master

    - ZF3 -> seguir procedimento
    
    https://olegkrivtsov.github.io/using-zend-framework-3-book/html/en/Creating_a_New_Module/How_to_Create_a_New_Module_.html


